<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        /* Center align the content */
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        /* Style for the container */
        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Reset Password</h1>
        <p>We've received a request to reset your password. Please use the following code to reset your password:</p>
        <h2>Reset Code: <%= validationCode %></h2>
        <p>If you didn't request this, you can ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br> The E-Commerce Platform Team</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
